---
layout: base.njk
title: Speaking
description: Talks by Roel van Bergen about agentic engineering, AI orchestration, mindfulness, and sustainable software development.
permalink: /talks/index.html
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<section class="page-hero speaking-hero">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="eyebrow mb-6">Talks and conference sessions</div>
    <h1>Making complex technology more explicit, practical, and human.</h1>
    <p class="page-lead">I speak about agentic software engineering, multi-agent systems, and attention under pressure. This page contains a small curated selection rather than every talk idea or submission.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-9">
      <a href="{{ site.sessionize }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="button-primary">View my Sessionize profile</a>
      <a href="{{ site.linkedin }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="button-secondary">Connect on LinkedIn</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
  <div class="section-intro mb-10">
    <div class="eyebrow">Showcased talks</div>
    <h2>Developed, presented, and ready for a new audience.</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="topic-list">
    {%- for talk in publicTalks -%}
    <article class="topic-card">
      <span class="topic-index">{% if loop.index < 10 %}0{% endif %}{{ loop.index }}</span>
      <div>
        <div class="talk-card-meta">
          <span class="talk-status">{{ talk.status }}</span>
          <span>{{ talk.audience }}</span>
        </div>
        <h2><a href="/talks/{{ talk.slug }}/">{{ talk.title }}</a></h2>
        <p>{{ talk.description }}</p>
        <p class="topic-outcome">{{ talk.takeaways[0] }}</p>
        <a href="/talks/{{ talk.slug }}/" class="text-link mt-5 inline-flex">View talk details</a>
      </div>
    </article>
    {%- else -%}
    <p>No talks are currently selected for the public showcase.</p>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-24">
  <div class="invitation-panel">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow mb-5">Invite me to speak</div>
      <h2>Conference, meetup, or an engineering team that wants to go deeper.</h2>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p>The sessions can be adapted to the audience, time slot, and technical depth. My Sessionize profile contains the current submission information; LinkedIn is the easiest place to start a conversation.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-7">
        <a href="{{ site.sessionize }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="button-primary">Open Sessionize</a>
        <a href="{{ site.linkedin }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="button-secondary">Connect on LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
